            <title>[GROOVY-4950] ConfigSlurper broken on AppEngine</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4950</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On the production AppEngine environment, ConfigSlurper now breaks in 1.8.1 (This was working in 1.8.0) This makes Groovy 1.8.1 unusable on GAE as it stands!&lt;/p&gt;

